@startuml
title C1 — System Context: OpenCode PrivateGPT Bridge MVP
left to right direction

actor "Developer" as developer
rectangle "OpenCode CLI\nCoding workflow and approvals" as opencode
rectangle "PrivateGPT Adapter\nLocal OpenAI-compatible bridge" as adapter
rectangle "PrivateGPT Platform\nModel, Agent and Conversation APIs" as privategpt
rectangle "Gemini 2.5 Pro" as model
rectangle "PrivateGPT Login Browser" as browser

developer --> opencode : runs and approves work
developer --> browser : authenticates
browser --> adapter : establishes session
opencode --> adapter : OpenAI-compatible HTTP
adapter --> privategpt : authenticated HTTPS\nAgent/model/conversation requests
privategpt --> model : inference
@enduml